    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD is a museum-grade example of rotary engineering. The 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged engine delivers smooth, linear power with exceptional compression. Featuring its original double-wishbone suspension and Torsen limited-slip differential, the handling remains razor-sharp. This unmodified specimen boasts factory-original paint and an immaculate interior, with all vacuum systems functioning to OEM specifications. A rare, mechanically perfect icon for the discerning collector.",
