      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving its flawless original paint and deep, swirl-free luster. The interior is immaculate, featuring supple leather with no signs of bolster wear, a smoke-free environment, and all factory electronics functioning perfectly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; it comes with a complete, documented service history and has never seen inclement weather. From the pristine, dust-free engine bay to the unmarked alloy wheels, every detail has been professionally attended to. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key masterpiece for the discerning enthusiast who demands the absolute best.",
