      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you my absolute pride and joy. Seriously, you won\u2019t find another one in this kind of shape\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, always kept it tucked away in the garage, and it's still sparkling inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. If you've been looking for that perfect, flawless ride, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take a look!",
