      "description": "Presenting an impeccable E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 power unit, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM valvetrain. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential, the drivetrain is mechanically flawless. The chassis has undergone preventative subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS overhaul to ensure long-term structural and timing integrity. Finished in original Laguna Seca Blue with pristine Nappa leather, this vehicle exhibits zero paint metamerism or interior bolster wear. A turn-key masterpiece for the purist seeking peak analog performance.",
